@baseUrl = http://localhost:5095

### Get Wallet Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Transaction History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/transactions
Accept: application/json

###

### Reset Wallet (Default $100)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": null
}

###

### Reset Wallet (Custom Amount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": 250.00
}

###

### Test Reserve Funds ($50)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00
}

###

### Test Reserve Funds ($25)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00
}

###

### Test Release Funds (Replace with actual TicketId from reserve response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00,
  "ticketId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Full Test Sequence
# 1. Get initial status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance

###

# 2. Reset wallet to $200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startingBalance": 200.00
}

###

# 3. Reserve $75
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 75.00
}

###

# 4. Check status after reserve
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance

###

# 5. Check transaction history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/transactions

